# .github/CODEOWNERS
#
# BGP++ GitHub Repository — Code Owners
# ======================================
#
# This file defines the default reviewers for pull requests based on
# which files are modified. GitHub will automatically request reviews
# from the listed owners when a PR touches matching paths.
#
# Rules:
#   - Later patterns take precedence over earlier ones.
#   - Any ONE listed owner can approve unless branch protection
#     requires multiple approvals.
#
# Team membership is managed via GitHub Teams
#
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Default — catches any file not matched by a more specific rule below.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*                                       @facebook/fboss-bgp

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Core Daemon — the main BGP++ service including session management,
# peer handling, route processing, and ASIC programming integration.
# Path: cpp/
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/cpp/                                   @facebook/fboss-bgp

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Thrift Interfaces — Thrift IDL definitions for the BGP++ service,
# including BGP structs, BMP structs, and streaming interfaces.
# Path: if/
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/if/                                    @facebook/fboss-bgp

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Libraries — shared libraries used across BGP++ components.
# Path: lib/
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/lib/                                   @facebook/fboss-bgp

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Documentation — protocol guides, developer guides, and design docs.
# Path: docs/
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/docs/                                  @facebook/fboss-bgp

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Tools — operational and development tooling for BGP++.
# Path: tools/
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/tools/                                 @facebook/fboss-bgp

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GitHub / Build — open-source build infrastructure, CI workflows,
# and GitHub-specific packaging.
# Path: github/
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/github/                                @facebook/fboss-bgp
